summary: This Mod adds some new Spellbreaker with other Design!
descriptionHtml:
Sorry for the bad english!
Do you also ever want to have a Spellbreaker with a other design?
Then this Mod is for you!

I think the normal design of the Spellbreaker is really ugly. So i made this mod.

This mod adds 7 new shields to the game located on the throat of the World. All the shields enchanted with Spellbreaker.

Adds:
Daedric Spellbreaker
Dragonbone Spellbreaker
Dragonscale Spellbreaker
Glass Spellbreaker
Ebony Spellbreaker
Dwarven Spellbreaker
Steel Spellbreaker

If you want other designs, post in comments.
Also check out my YouTube Channel:
http://www.youtube.com/channel/UC0ZZBwiZyMRDa0NYsHH2moQ/videos?flow=grid&view=0
And my other Mods!
I hope you like it!

STORMBOW
author: Stormbow123
